HEADWORD: Enlightener
<hw>En*light"en*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
enlightens or illuminates; one who, or that which, communicates light to
the eye, or clear views to the mind.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>enlightening</ent>⟦br⟧
